title: B.C. records 2 more COVID-19 deaths and 67 new cases, bringing total to 792
description: Another two people have died of COVID-19 in B.C., bringing the province's total to 16 deaths caused by the virus.
content:
Another two people have died of COVID-19 in B.C., bringing the province's total to 16 deaths caused by the virus.
